  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      compton is a compositor for X11, based on xcompmgr. In addition to
      shadows, fading and translucency, compton implements window frame opacity
      control, inactive window transparency, and shadows on argb windows. 
    </para>

