  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      No proper tarballs have been generated by the maintainers yet. To obtain
      the source code, clone the compton git repository:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>git clone git://github.com/chjj/compton &amp;&amp;
cd compton</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install compton by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make PREFIX=/usr NO_DBUS=1</userinput></screen>
<!--
sed -i -e '/^install/ s/docs//' \
       -e '/install.*MANPAGES/ s/^/#/' Makefile
-->

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make PREFIX=/usr NO_DBUS=1 install</userinput></screen>

<!--
